<section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125928" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(110, 106, 104); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(250, 206, 88); visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); visibility: visible;"><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125936" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); display: flex; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;">08</strong></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: -7px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 20.8229px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 6px; overflow: hidden; visibility: visible;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"/></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 13px; visibility: visible;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 22 79" style="display: block; visibility: visible;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: rgb(214, 214, 214); fill-rule: evenodd; visibility: visible;" d="M4173,595h22l-6,13,6,13-8,5,4.82,5.179L4190,637l3,11-7,12,6,14h-19V595Z" transform="translate(-4173 -595)"></path><path style="fill: rgb(243, 243, 243); fill-rule: evenodd; visibility: visible;" d="M4173,595h22l-10,13,8,13-12,5,9,5-4,6,4,10-9,13,8,14h-16V595Z" transform="translate(-4173 -595)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 13px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); visibility: visible;"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; visibility: visible;">教学工作诊断与改进的目标任务是建立什么机制？&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; visibility: visible;">建立基于高职院校人才培养工作状态数据、学校自主诊改、省教育厅根据需要抽样复核的工作机制。&nbsp;</span></p></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 635px; visibility: visible;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 580 22" style="display: block; visibility: visible;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: rgb(214, 214, 214); fill-rule: evenodd; visibility: visible;" d="M3783,2630h580v21l-18.27-3.44-26.27,2.36L4280,2643l-33.09,5.2L4198,2648l-40,4-35-8-40,7-46-7-24,6-37-5-29,4-21-8-36,7-28-4-25,4-31-6-23,2v-14Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path><path style="fill: rgb(247, 247, 247); fill-rule: evenodd; visibility: visible;" d="M3783,2630h580v19l-18.27-6.45-26.27,2.37L4280,2638l-33.09,10.2L4198,2644l-39.91,6.05L4123,2642l-40,7-47-9-22.79,6.55L3976,2639l-29.2,7.95L3926,2637l-36,9-28-6-25,6-31-9-23,5v-12Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section><p></p><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125928" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(110, 106, 104); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(250, 206, 88); visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0; visibility: visible;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); visibility: visible;"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;">09</strong></section></section></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 13px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247); visibility: visible;"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; visibility: visible;">全国教学工作诊断与改进的目标任务是什么？&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; visibility: visible; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun; visibility: visible;">是促进高职院校在建立教学工作诊断与改进制度基础上，构建网络化、全覆盖、具有较强预警功能和激励作用的内部质量保证体系，实现教学管理水平和人才培养质量的持续提升。</span></p></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 635px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 580 22" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #d6d6d6;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v21l-18.27-3.44-26.27,2.36L4280,2643l-33.09,5.2L4198,2648l-40,4-35-8-40,7-46-7-24,6-37-5-29,4-21-8-36,7-28-4-25,4-31-6-23,2v-14Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path><path style="fill: #f7f7f7;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v19l-18.27-6.45-26.27,2.37L4280,2638l-33.09,10.2L4198,2644l-39.91,6.05L4123,2642l-40,7-47-9-22.79,6.55L3976,2639l-29.2,7.95L3926,2637l-36,9-28-6-25,6-31-9-23,5v-12Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125928" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(110, 106, 104); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(250, 206, 88);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">10</strong></section></section></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 13px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">国家教学工作诊断与改进的具体目标任务是什么？&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（1）完善高职院校内部质量保证体系。重点在于高职院校在学校、专业、课程、教师、学生不同层面建立起完整且相对独立的自我质量保证机制。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（2）提升教育教学管理信息化水平。重点在于高职院校进一步加强人才培养工作状态数据管理系统的建设与应用，完善预警功能，提升学校教学运行管理信息化水平。&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（3）树立现代质量文化。重点在于高职院校提升质量意识，建立完善质量标准体系、不断提升标准内涵，促进全员、全过程、全方位育人。</span></p></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 635px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 580 22" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #d6d6d6;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v21l-18.27-3.44-26.27,2.36L4280,2643l-33.09,5.2L4198,2648l-40,4-35-8-40,7-46-7-24,6-37-5-29,4-21-8-36,7-28-4-25,4-31-6-23,2v-14Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path><path style="fill: #f7f7f7;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v19l-18.27-6.45-26.27,2.37L4280,2638l-33.09,10.2L4198,2644l-39.91,6.05L4123,2642l-40,7-47-9-22.79,6.55L3976,2639l-29.2,7.95L3926,2637l-36,9-28-6-25,6-31-9-23,5v-12Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125928" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(110, 106, 104); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(250, 206, 88);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><section data-role="title" data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125936" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; background-color: rgb(243, 243, 243); display: flex;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: space-around; align-items: center; flex-direction: column;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 4px; height: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 6px; height: 6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 4px; height: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 6px; height: 6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 4px; height: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 6px; height: 6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; align-items: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 4px; height: 3px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 6px; height: 6px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">11</strong></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: -7px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 20.8229px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); height: 6px; overflow: hidden;"><br style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"/></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 13px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 22 79" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #d6d6d6;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M4173,595h22l-6,13,6,13-8,5,4.82,5.179L4190,637l3,11-7,12,6,14h-19V595Z" transform="translate(-4173 -595)"></path><path style="fill: #f3f3f3;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M4173,595h22l-10,13,8,13-12,5,9,5-4,6,4,10-9,13,8,14h-16V595Z" transform="translate(-4173 -595)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 13px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">教学工作诊断与改进的具体目标任务是什么？&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（1）完善高职院校内部质量保证体系&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（2）树立现代质量文化&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（3）推进高职院校特色发展&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（4）提升教育教学管理信息化水平&nbsp;</span></p></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 635px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 580 22" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #d6d6d6;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v21l-18.27-3.44-26.27,2.36L4280,2643l-33.09,5.2L4198,2648l-40,4-35-8-40,7-46-7-24,6-37-5-29,4-21-8-36,7-28-4-25,4-31-6-23,2v-14Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path><path style="fill: #f7f7f7;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v19l-18.27-6.45-26.27,2.37L4280,2638l-33.09,10.2L4198,2644l-39.91,6.05L4123,2642l-40,7-47-9-22.79,6.55L3976,2639l-29.2,7.95L3926,2637l-36,9-28-6-25,6-31-9-23,5v-12Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125928" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(110, 106, 104); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(250, 206, 88);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">12</strong></section></section></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 13px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">国家教学工作诊断与改进的基本原则是什么？&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（1）数据分析与实际调研相结合&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（2）坚持标准与注重特色相结合&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">（3）自主诊改与抽样复核相结合&nbsp;</span></p></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 635px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 580 22" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #d6d6d6;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v21l-18.27-3.44-26.27,2.36L4280,2643l-33.09,5.2L4198,2648l-40,4-35-8-40,7-46-7-24,6-37-5-29,4-21-8-36,7-28-4-25,4-31-6-23,2v-14Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path><path style="fill: #f7f7f7;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v19l-18.27-6.45-26.27,2.37L4280,2638l-33.09,10.2L4198,2644l-39.91,6.05L4123,2642l-40,7-47-9-22.79,6.55L3976,2639l-29.2,7.95L3926,2637l-36,9-28-6-25,6-31-9-23,5v-12Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125928" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(110, 106, 104); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(250, 206, 88);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">13</strong></section></section></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 13px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"><p style="margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; text-indent: 2em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">教学工作诊断与改进是指学校根据自身办学理念、办学定位、人才培养目标，聚焦专业设置与条件、教师队伍与建设、课程体系与改革、课堂教学与实践、学校管理与制度、校企合作与创新、质量监控与成效等人才培养工作要素，查找不足与完善提高的工作过程。</span></p></section><section data-width="100%" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; width: 635px;"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="100%" height="100%" viewbox="0 0 580 22" style="display: block;" data-height="100%"><path style="fill: #d6d6d6;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v21l-18.27-3.44-26.27,2.36L4280,2643l-33.09,5.2L4198,2648l-40,4-35-8-40,7-46-7-24,6-37-5-29,4-21-8-36,7-28-4-25,4-31-6-23,2v-14Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path><path style="fill: #f7f7f7;fill-rule: evenodd;" d="M3783,2630h580v19l-18.27-6.45-26.27,2.37L4280,2638l-33.09,10.2L4198,2644l-39.91,6.05L4123,2642l-40,7-47-9-22.79,6.55L3976,2639l-29.2,7.95L3926,2637l-36,9-28-6-25,6-31-9-23,5v-12Z" transform="translate(-3783 -2630)"></path></svg></section></section></section></section><section data-tools="135编辑器" data-id="125928" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(110, 106, 104); font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; display: flex; border-bottom: 1px solid rgb(250, 206, 88);"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; flex-shrink: 0;"><section style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 16px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51);"><strong data-brushtype="text" style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;">14</strong></section></section></section><section style="margin: 3px 0px 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><section data-autoskip="1" style="margin: 0px; padding: 10px 13px 5px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); background-color: rgb(247, 247, 247);"><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">全国诊改专委会2019 年第一次全体会议暨诊改复核工作研讨培训会上谢俐副司长提出，应把握全局，按新时代职业教育的新要求系统推进诊改工作，做到：一个核心、两个主体、三个过程、四个阶段、五个转变的主攻方向、六个化的目标，分别是指什么？&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">一个核心：即持续提高质量；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">两个主体：即学校和省级教育行政部门；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">三个过程：即事前、事中、事后；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">四个阶段：即制度、机制、能力、文化；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">五个转变的主攻方向：即管理变治理、被动变主动、零散变系统、主观变客观、一时变日常；&nbsp;</span></p><p style="margin: 0px 10px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); font-size: 15px; letter-spacing: 1px; line-height: 2em; text-indent: 2em; font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, Arial, sans-serif; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;"><span style="margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; font-family: 宋体, SimSun;">六个化的目标：即治理体系最优化，管理工作标准化，教学秩序正规化，实现手段信息化，质量保障可控化，治理能力现代化。</span></p></section></section></section></section><p></p><p><br/></p>